title: Breakfast
itunes:title: Breakfast
description:
In this episode, Bobby and Sophie explore "Breakfast"!

Bobby cooks his famous scrambled eggs for Sophie, then they dig into everything from meats, to cultural traditions, to why breakfast sandwiches are so satisfying.

Follow Host’s Bobby Flay and Sophie Flay on instagram to get future updates on their brand new podcast, “Always Hungry” from iHeartRadio. 

Bobby Flay: https://www.instagram.com/bobbyflay

Sophie Flay: https://www.instagram.com/abc7sophie
